Bongo star Diamond Platimumz' wife Tanasha Donna officially launched her EP in a star-studded affair at the Sarit Centre Expo on January 31. The 24-year-old's mini-album, titled 'Donna Tella', features collaborations with Kenya's Khaligraph Jones and Diamond Platinumz. The launch was attended by the who's who in the East African showbiz industry, among them Nameless and Wahu, Bahati and wife Diana Marwa, Khaligraph Jones, Nadia Mukami, Tanzanian DJ Romy Jones and Bonfire Adventures couple Simon and Sarah Kabu.